<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">8.How this Policy is updated</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">9.How to contact us</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">Please read and understand this Policy carefully before using our products (or services).</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">1.&nbsp;<u style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 186, 0);">How we collect and use your personal data</u></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">Personal data means any information relating to an identified or identifiable natural person (&quot;data subject&quot;);&nbsp;an identifiable natural person is one who can be identified, directly or indirectly, in particular by reference to an identifier such as a name, an identification number, location data, an online identifier or one or more factors specific to physical aspects, physiological, genetic, mental, economic, cultural or social identity of that natural person.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">We will collect and use your personal data only for the following purposes here:</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">1.1 Information required regarding the use of Granyupon services</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">Our services contain certain basic functions, including making your purchases online, improving your experience of our services, and ensuring secure transactions.&nbsp;To perform such functions, we may collect and use the following information related to you:</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">1.1.1 Granyupon account information</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">You must use a Granyupon account to allow access and use of the Granyupon platform.&nbsp;When you register or log in to the Granyupon platform, you must provide the following account information to complete the registration or log in: an email address or the account and password (OF YOUR CHOICE).</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">1.1.2 Communication information</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">To ensure your communication with the sellers in the course of the transaction and your consultation and obtaining evidence of said communication history, the system of the Granyupon platform will automatically collect and store your information in the box on the Granyupon platform.&nbsp;Unless we are required to use or disclose such information as explicitly required by you or in accordance with relevant applicable laws, we will not use or disclose such information in any way.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">In addition, to help you better manage rights protection and after-sales services with respect to traded goods, you may be required to provide us with your personal telephone number to receive timely feedback on handling results and relevant information.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">1.1.3 Financial information</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">To use the payment services, you must provide the following financial information to complete payments, ensure transaction security, and comply with relevant applicable laws: billing address and bank account.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">1.1.4 Transaction information</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">To ensure the delivery of goods and services, you must provide the following information for the timely receipt of goods / services and inquiries and verification of the status of the transaction: name, personal telephone number, delivery address, transaction record and information from the order.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">1.1.5 IP address, device information, etc.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">For your convenience in quickly searching for the products you are interested in, we may collect common data from the device you use (hardware serial number, MAC address, unique device ID, etc.), language settings, IP address, and browsing history on the site of your every visit on the Granyupon platform.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">In addition, such information can also be collected and used for data analysis and study, for justified needs to offer personalized services and improve service quality, to improve the security of our services system, for a more precise prevention of fraud. on phishing sites and to ensure the security of your Granyupon account.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">1.1.6 The above information that you provide is authorized for our continued use as long as you use our services.&nbsp;If you request the closure of an account or justified deletion, we will stop using and deleting such information in accordance with relevant laws.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">1.2 Information you provide us at your choice</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">To enhance your experience of our services, you may choose to provide the following personal information to purchase the following additional services.&nbsp;If you choose not to provide such personal data, your use of the main functions of the Granyupon services will not be affected, but you may not be able to use such additional services or you may be asked to fill in certain information each time you use certain services:</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">1.2.1 Personalized recommendation and sending of promotional and marketing information</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">During the use of our services, at any time you can provide or choose to delete the following additional information that helps us offer more relevant services and experiences: name, gender, country / jurisdiction, date of birth, date of birth of spouse / parents , important anniversaries, income level, tags, third-party social media accounts, etc.&nbsp;Such information will be used to analyze your behaviors and preferences in order to tailor personalized services for you and to send you special offers, marketing information, advertisements or other information that you may be interested in.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">1.2.2 Other information</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">If you want, you can comment on the products / services you buy.&nbsp;These comments will be used to shape the testimonials of the corresponding products for reference by other Granyupon users and to optimize the user experience of the relevant services.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">If you use an Android device, you can, at your option, provide us with location data to access real-time information from merchants in your surrounding area and purchase site language services that match your location.&nbsp;You can also, at your choice, provide us with your SIM card details (including contact list) according to your needs, so that you can add and / or communicate with other Granyupon users in a timely manner.&nbsp;At any time you can close the relevant functions and immediately stop providing location data or SIM card data on your Android system or our app.&nbsp;Once you have closed those functions, we will stop collecting and using your personal data as mentioned above and we will stop offering you relevant services.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">1.3 We will seek your prior consent if we intend to use such information for other purposes not covered in this document or to use the information for purposes other than the particular purposes for which it is collected.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">2.&nbsp;<u style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 186, 0);">How we use cookies and similar technologies</u></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">2.1 Cookie</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">To ensure the smooth functioning of the website and meet your personalized demands, we will store a small file called Cookie on your computer or mobile devices.&nbsp;Generally, the cookie includes identifiers, name of the site and some numbers and characters.&nbsp;Under Cookie, the website can store your preferences or products in the cart and other data, in order to provide you with a preference setting for purchases, help you optimize the selection and interaction of ads, help you judge your registration status and account security, etc.&nbsp;.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">We will not use cookies for any other purpose than this Policy.&nbsp;You can manage or delete cookies according to your preferences.&nbsp;For relevant details, see AboutCookies.org.&nbsp;You can delete all cookies stored on your computer, since most web browsers have the function of preventing cookies.&nbsp;If you do, you must change your user settings in person each time you visit our website.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">2.2 Website beacon and pixel tag &nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">In addition to cookies, we will apply the website beacon, pixel tag, and other similar technologies to the website.&nbsp;For example, the email we send you may include a URL that links to content on our website.&nbsp;If you click on such a link, we may track your click, to help us understand your product or service preferences and improve customer services.&nbsp;Generally, a website beacon is a kind of transparent image embedded in a website or email.&nbsp;By virtue of the pixel tag in the email, we can know whether the email is open or not.&nbsp;If you do not want to be tracked by this method, you can unsubscribe from the mailing list at any time.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">2.3 Do not track &nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">Several web browsers have Do Not Track, which can issue Do Not Track requests to websites.&nbsp;At present, the major Internet standards organizations have not established relevant policies on how websites deal with such a request.&nbsp;However, if your browser starts using Do Not Track, all of our websites will respect your choice.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">3.&nbsp;<u style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 186, 0);">Third party data processor</u></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">In accordance with our own business demands, we will entrust your personal data to a third party data processor in a way that complies with GDPR requirements, in order to provide better customer service, ensure the security of transactions and improve the user experience. .&nbsp;For example, the data processor may help us verify your identity and conduct a background investigation, police investigation, fraud prevention, and risk assessment to ensure the security of your account and the security of transactions, and help us to provide a logistics service so that you can receive the corresponding goods / services among others in a timely manner</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">We entrust your personal data to the data processor only for legal, adequate, necessary, specific and clear purposes, and we process personal data necessary for the provision of the service only.&nbsp;We will do our best to supervise the data processor to fully execute the entrustment agreement for processing legally, in order to ensure that your rights can be guaranteed to the fullest extent possible.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">4.&nbsp;<u style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 186, 0);">Public disclosure</u></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">4.1 We will publicly disclose your personal data only in the following situations: &nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">4.1.1 Obtain your explicit consent; &nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">4.1.2 Law-based disclosure: We may publicly disclose your personal data if required to do so by laws, legal procedures, lawsuits, or competent government authorities.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">5.&nbsp;<u style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 186, 0);">How we protect your personal data</u></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">5.1 We have used security protection measures that comply with industry standards to protect the personal data provided by you and prevent unauthorized access, public disclosure, use, modification, damage or loss of data.&nbsp;We will take all reasonable and practicable steps to protect your personal data.&nbsp;For example, your browser is under SSL encryption protection when you exchange data (such as credit card information) with &quot;service&quot;;&nbsp;meanwhile, we will provide https secure browsing methods to the Granyupon website;&nbsp;We will use an encryption technique to ensure the confidentiality of the data and we will store personal and non-personal data separately;&nbsp;we will use a reliable protection mechanism to prevent hostile attacks on data;&nbsp;We will implement an access control mechanism to ensure that only authorized personnel have access to personal data; &nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">5.2 We will take all reasonable and practicable steps to ensure that irrelevant personal data is not collected.&nbsp;We will reserve your personal data only within the period necessary to achieve the objectives established in this Policy, except for an extension of the reservation period or permitted by law. &nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">5.3 We will periodically update and publish the relevant content on security risk, personal data security impact assessment and other reports.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">5.4 Since the Internet is not an absolutely secure environment in which Granyupon&#39;s e-mails, instant messaging and other user exchange methods.&nbsp;During this communication process, the personal data that you voluntarily provide or describe may be disclosed to others.&nbsp;We strongly recommend that you do not submit personal data using this method.&nbsp;Please use a complex password to help us protect your account to be safe. &nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">5.5 We will do everything possible to ensure or guarantee the security of any information you send us.&nbsp;We will assume appropriate legal responsibilities if your legal rights and interests are compromised due to unauthorized access, public disclosure, tampering, or damage to information as a result of our damaged physical, technical, or managerial safeguards.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">5.6 After the leakage of personal data, in accordance with laws and regulations, we will inform you of our contact information, basic situation of the security event and possible impacts, actions we take or to take, relevant suggestions for prevention and self-directed risk .&nbsp;reduction, remedies for you, among others, in a timely manner.&nbsp;We will inform you of the situation relevant to the event via email, letter, call, push notification and other ways in a timely manner, or in the event that it is difficult to inform the subjects of personal data one by one, we will publish the advertisement in a reasonable and effective manner. &nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">5.7 In addition, we will promptly inform the deletion of the personal data security event in accordance with the requirements of the supervision department. &nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">6.&nbsp;<u style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 186, 0);">Your rights</u></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">In accordance with applicable laws, regulations, standards and their established practices, we guarantee that you can exercise the following rights over your personal data:</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.1 Right of access</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">You have the right to access your personal data described in Article 1 and Article 2 of this Policy through the configuration of your personal account, except for the exceptions provided by laws and regulations.&nbsp;The information you can access includes, but is not limited to, the types of personal data that we collect and process, the purpose of processing such personal data (and the consequences of not providing such personal data), basis of legitimacy, facts of leaving the country, storage period, right and channel to file a complaint, and we will inform you of the specific data profiling logic if we use your personal data for data profiling.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">If you are unable to access your personal data through the methods mentioned above, please feel free to email us at [info@granyupon.com].&nbsp;We will respond to your request for access within 30 days.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">For other personal data generated during the process of using our products or services, as long as it does not cost us too much, we will provide you with electronic copies of your personal data in accordance with the requirements of the GDPR.&nbsp;If you wish to exercise your right of access to data, send an email to [info@granyupon.com].&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.2 Correction of inaccurate or incomplete personal data</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">You can correct or supplement some of your personal data through your personal account settings yourself.&nbsp;You have an obligation to update your personal data in a timely manner.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">Correction of certain special information is probably not possible for you.&nbsp;You can communicate with us through various contact details published in this Policy or on the Granyupon platform.&nbsp;We will respond to your request for access within 30 days.&nbsp;To ensure the security of your account, we may ask you to verify your identity.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.3 Deletion of your personal data</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.3.1 You can ask us to delete your personal data in the following cases: &nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">a) The relevant data is no longer necessary for collection or processing, and we have no legal basis to continue processing your personal data;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">b) You no longer accept or refuse to allow us to process your personal data, and we have no legal basis to continue to process your personal data;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">c) Our processing of personal data violates laws and regulations;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">d) Your data is related to the data of any child;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">e) You no longer use our products or services, or have closed your account;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">f) We no longer provide products or services to you.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.3.2 If we decide to respond to your request for erasure, we will inform the third party that we have taken it upon ourselves to process your personal data to the extent possible and will require such third parties to erase your personal data in a timely manner, unless we do so. contrary.&nbsp;provided by laws and regulations, or such third parties have obtained your independent authorization.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.3.3 Notwithstanding the foregoing, to resolve disputes, enforce user agreements, and comply with technical requirements related to secure operation, we may still retain certain data for a reasonable time to the extent permitted by law.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.4 Withdrawal of consents and processing restrictions</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.4.1 For the personal data that you have allowed us to collect and process, you can withdraw your consent at any time through your account settings or send an email to [info@granyupon.com], indicating which consent you wish to revoke.&nbsp;When you have withdrawn your consent, we will no longer process the relevant personal data.&nbsp;However, your decision to withdraw your consent will not affect the lawfulness of the processing of personal data previously carried out on the basis of your authorization. &nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.4.2 In addition, in some jurisdictions, applicable law may authorize you to limit how we use your personal data, including:</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">a) Doubts about the accuracy of your personal data;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">b) The processing of personal data is illegal and you only request to restrict the use of your personal data and to oppose the deletion of your personal data;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">c) We no longer need your personal data for processing, but you need such information in order to file a claim or respond to a claim;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">d) You object to our processing your personal data based on public interests or legitimate interests and you object to waiting for verification whether the aforementioned public interests or the legitimate interests of Granyupon will prevail over your own interests.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.5 Right of refusal</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.5.1 In some jurisdictions, applicable law may authorize you to require that Granyupon not process your personal data for a specific purpose (including identifying behavior analysis, direct marketing purposes, etc.), although such processing is based on interests. legitimate.&nbsp;If you object to such processing, we will no longer process your personal data for these purposes unless we can demonstrate that such processing has a compelling and reasonable cause, or that such processing is necessary for the establishment, exercise or safeguarding of legal rights.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.5.2 If your personal data is processed for direct marketing purposes, you can refuse to allow Granyupon to process your data for direct marketing purposes at any time via the start settings on the relevant advertising screen or by sending an email to [info@granyupon.com].</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.6 Cancel an account</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.6.1 You can cancel the Granyupon account you have registered at any time.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.6.2 After canceling your account, we will stop providing you services and delete your personal data within the time limit stipulated by applicable laws in accordance with your request, unless the laws and regulations provide otherwise or when you have reached a agreement with us.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.7 Obtain a copy of personal data</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.7.1 You have the right to send us a written request to obtain a copy of your personal data through the contact information published in this Policy.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.7.2 We may also directly transmit the copy of your personal data to a third party designated by you in accordance with your requirements and existing communication technology under the condition that it is technically feasible, such as that the data interfaces match.&nbsp;If said third party refuses to receive the copy of your personal data, resulting in a transmission failure, you must coordinate with said third party on your own and Granyupon will not be responsible for the transmission failure.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.8 Limitation of automatic decision-making of the information system (data image)</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.8.1 Based on personal data legally collected under authorization, automatic decisions (for example, sending commercial information) made by tagging or image processing made through non-artificial automatic decision-making technologies, such as the information and the algorithm, will be subject to your legal restrictions.&nbsp;In some business functions, we can only make decisions based on a non-artificial automatic decision-making mechanism, such as the information system and algorithm.&nbsp;Where these decisions significantly influence your legal rights and interests, you have the right to ask us to explain or reject our continued provision of such image processing or tagging service,</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.9 Respond to your previous request</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.9.1 To ensure security, you may need to submit a request in writing or prove your identity.&nbsp;We may ask you to verify your identity before processing your request.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.9.2 We will respond to you within 30 days.&nbsp;If you are not satisfied, you can also file a claim in the manner provided for in Article 0 of this Agreement.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.9.3 For your reasonable request, we do not charge any fees in principle, but we will charge a certain cost for repeated requests beyond the reasonable limit, as the case may be.&nbsp;We may reject those repeated requests without cause, requests that require too much technical means (for example, a new system development or a fundamental change to existing practice is necessary) or that pose risks to the legal rights and interests of others, or extremely unrealistic requests.&nbsp;(for example, involving information stored on the backup tape).</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.10 We will not be able to respond to your request as required by laws and regulations, in the following situations:</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.10.1 Directly related to national security and national defense security;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.10.2 Directly related to public safety, public health and the main public interests;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.10.3 Directly related to criminal investigation, prosecution, trial, execution of sentences, etc .;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.10.4 There is sufficient evidence to demonstrate their subjective malice or abuse of rights;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.10.5 Responding to your request will result in serious harm to your rights and legitimate interests or those of annoying individuals or organizations.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.10.6 Involve trade secrets;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">6.10.7 Other circumstances specified by applicable laws.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">7.&nbsp;<u style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 186, 0);">How we process children&#39;s personal data</u></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">7.1 Our products, websites and services are for adults only.&nbsp;Children should not create their own user accounts.&nbsp;We will not collect or use data about children, if we are informed.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">7.2 We consider anyone under [18] years of age to be a child, despite the different definitions of a child by local laws and customs.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">7.3 Once we have collected personal data about children without the prior and verifiable consent of their parents, we will try to delete the relevant data as soon as possible.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">8.&nbsp;<u style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 186, 0);">How your personal data is transferred across borders</u></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;In principle, the personal data collected and generated by us will be stored in the [People&#39;s Republic of China].&nbsp;We hereby draw your attention to the fact that the People&#39;s Republic of China is not a third country that meets the &quot;standard of full protection&quot; as identified by the European Commission.&nbsp;We will do everything possible to provide adequate guarantees for the transfer of your personal data and to satisfy the exercise of your rights and access to effective legal remedies.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">You should have a complete understanding of such risks and you hereby authorize us to transfer your personal data to the foreign jurisdictions of the country or region where you use the service, including China.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">9.&nbsp;<u style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 186, 0);">How is this Policy updated?</u></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">9.1&nbsp;</strong> We reserve the right to adjust this Policy at any time in accordance with changes in services, adjustments to applicable laws and policies, as well as other affected factors.&nbsp;We will not reduce your rights under this Privacy Policy without your express consent.&nbsp;Any update to this Policy will be posted on this web page to mark the update time,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">so do not hesitate to view and understand the privacy policy that you should observe.&nbsp;If you do not agree to accept this Policy, stop visiting and using our services.</strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">9.2 For major changes, we will also provide a more noticeable notice (including an email notification explaining specific changes to the privacy policy for certain services).</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">9.3 Important changes referenced in this Policy include, but are not limited to:</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">9.3.1 Major changes in our service model.&nbsp;For example, the purpose of the processing of personal data, the type of personal data processed, the use of personal data, etc .;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">9.3.2 Important changes in our ownership structure, organizational structure, among others.&nbsp;Such as, change of ownership caused by business adjustment, bankruptcy and mergers and acquisitions, and others;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">9.3.3 Changes to the main objects of the personal data delegated to be processed;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">9.3.4 Changes in the main objects of personal data disclosed publicly;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">9.3.5 Important changes to your rights to participate in the processing of personal data and how it is exercised;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">9.3.6 Faced with changes in our department responsible for treating the security of personal data, contact information and complaint channels;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">9.3.7 Faced with high risks indicated in the evaluation report of the impact of the security of personal data.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">9.4 We will also archive the previous version of this Policy for your reference.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;">10.&nbsp;<u style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 186, 0);">How to contact us</u></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">10.1 Please contact us through the form in the footer, if you have any questions, suggestions or complaints about our privacy policy.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 16.05px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">10.2 We will generally respond within [30 days]. If you are not satisfied with our response, especially if you believe that our acts of processing personal data have caused harm to your legal rights and interests, you can also contact the [relevant EU data protection authority or committee] for assistance .</p>
    
